Distribution. This species is distributed along the Adriatic shore from southern Dalmatia (Omiš) to northwestern Albania (Mt. Renc). Very frequent in the Kotor Bay area and in the Rumija Mts (
Boeters et al . 1989
). Inland it spreads up into the Morača Valley in Montenegro and into the valleys of Cem, Kir and Drin Rivers in Albania ( Fig. 1D ).
